RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT a.Product_Code, a.Product_Description FROM Oltms_Product a WHERE Module = 'TL' AND Product_Type = 'T' AND Record_Stat = 'O' AND Auth_Stat = 'A' AND a.Product_Code IN (SELECT c.Product_Code FROM Olvw_Avl_Prod_Br_Usr c, Olvw_User_Products s WHERE s.User_Id = c.User_Id AND s.Product_Code = c.Product_Code AND a.Product_Code = c.Product_Code AND s.User_Id = Global.User_Id) ORDER BY 1

SELECT a.Position_Identifier, a.Portfolio, a.Branch, a.Desk_Code, a.Position_Qualifier, Decode(a.Identifier_Type, 'W', 'Swap', 'T', 'Silent', 'S', 'Self') Identifier_Type, a.Firm_Acct_Mnemonic FROM Tlvws_Position_Detail a WHERE a.Branch = Global.Current_Branch AND a.Record_Stat = 'O' AND A.Identifier_Type NOT IN ('W') AND A.desk_type NOT IN ('O','T') AND a.Auth_Stat = 'A' ORDER BY 1
SELECT Ccy_Code, Ccy_Name FROM Cytms_Ccy_Defn WHERE Record_Stat = 'O' AND Auth_Stat = 'A' ORDER BY 1
SELECT Expense_Code FROM Tltm_Portfolio_Expcode_Detail WHERE Portfolio = ?
SELECT b.Customer_No, b.Customer_Name1, b.Short_Name FROM Oltms_Customer b WHERE b.Auth_Stat = 'A' AND b.Record_Stat = 'O' ORDER BY 1
SELECT Broker, NAME FROM Bktms_Brmaster WHERE Record_Stat = 'O' AND Auth_Stat = 'A' ORDER BY Broker

SELECT DISTINCT Cusip_No FROM Oltbs_Contract_Master WHERE Contract_Ref_No IN (SELECT Borrower_Ref_No FROM Lbtbs_Part_Proc_Stat WHERE Counterparty = ?) AND Product_Type = 'C' AND Cusip_No IN (SELECT a.Cusip_No FROM Oltbs_Contract_Master a,Olvw_Avl_Prod_Br_Usr c,Olvw_User_Products s WHERE s.User_Id = c.User_Id AND s.Product_Code = c.Product_Code AND a.Product = c.Product_Code AND a.Branch = c.Branch_Code AND a.Product_Type = 'C' AND a.Module = 'LB' AND s.User_Id = Global.User_Id)

RAD_DATASOURCES.RELATION_WITH_PARENT: TLTBS_TICKET_TRADE_MASTER.TICKET_ID = TLTBS_TICKET_TRADE_MASTER__SSI.TICKET_ID AND TLTBS_TICKET_TRADE_MASTER.SOURCE_CODE = TLTBS_TICKET_TRADE_MASTER__SSI.SOURCE_CODE AND TLTBS_TICKET_TRADE_MASTER.BRANCH = TLTBS_TICKET_TRADE_MASTER__SSI.BRANCH

RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT A.ccy_code, A.ccy_name FROM cytms_ccy_defn A WHERE A.ccy_code NOT IN (SELECT CURRENCY FROM TLTBS_UPLOAD_SSI B WHERE B.EXT_CONTRACT_REF_NO = ? AND CUSTOMER_NO = ?) AND A.record_stat = 'O' AND A.auth_stat = 'A' ORDER BY 1
SELECT Ssi_Mnemonic,Currency,Counterparty,Settlement_Seq_No FROM Oltm_Instr WHERE Branch = 'ALL' AND Module = 'AL' AND Counterparty = ? AND Currency = '*.*' AND Product_Code = 'ALL' ORDER BY 3,2
